t_audio_discussion_question_1::clip_card: Gaafadhu: Waa'ee namichaa yaada akkamii qabda?
Gaafadhu: Waa'ee namichaa yaada akkamii qabda?
t_audio_discussion_question_1::text_card: Mareen namoota baayyee gaaffii tokko gaafachuurratti marsee jira. Qajoojiin kun namoota baayyee nama tokkorratti akka isaan yaada isaanii kannan gaafata. Mareen yaadota waa'ee nama beekamtii aadaa yookaan hawaasaa cimaa qabuu sassaabuudhaan akka gaariitti hojjeta. Caalmaatti naaf hojjeta jettee yoo yaadde bilisa ta'uudhaan gaaffii filannoof ta'u fayyadami.
t_audio_discussion_question_1::clip_card: Sagalee Bakka qaamichaaf barbaachisaa ta'ee waraabi.
t_audio_discussion_question_1::text_card: Bakka \“namicha\” kan jedhu argitetti maqaa namicha xiyyeeffannoon irra jiruutiin bakka buusuu barbaaduu dandeessa.
